room_title: Escape room "Locked! in the Asylum" by Locked! Evansville in Evansville
room_address: 3101 N Green River Road Suite 140 Evansville, IN 47715
room_description: Something isn't right at the Evansville Institute. An old friend is missing, and his file has mysteriously disappeared. A routine visit results in your group Locked! in the director's office. Can you reconstruct the director's nefarious plans and escape before you find yourselves committed?
